sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant A as Agent Runtime (LLM + Orchestrator)
  participant MCP as MCP Client
  participant G as Context Gateway (MCP Server)
  participant T as External Tool (Playwright/GitHub/Logs)
  participant S as Raw Artifact Store (optional)

  A->>MCP: tool.call(args)
  MCP->>G: tool.call(args)
  G->>T: execute tool(args)
  T-->>G: raw_output (large)
  G->>S: store(raw_output)
  S-->>G: artifact_uri
  G-->>G: compress/extract(raw_output)
  G-->>MCP: compact_output + artifact_uri
  MCP-->>A: compact_output + artifact_uri
  Note over A: Only compact_output enters
  Note over A: the LLM context window
